1	//! Byte-parity tests. Each fixture in tests/fixtures/ is an OBSERVED oracle
2	//! WARNING block (from `wf_oracle.sh` on the correspondingly-named probe). We
3	//! build the matching AST by hand and assert that render_report(check_theory)
4	//! reproduces the oracle output byte-for-byte.
